---
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_TAGLINE } from '../consts';
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="footer">
	<div class="container footer-grid">

		<div class="col col-brand">
			<div class="masthead-mark">
				<span class="brand-ko">{SITE_TITLE}</span>
				<span class="brand-en">MIGUK&nbsp;STORY</span>
			</div>
			<p class="tagline">{SITE_TAGLINE}</p>
		</div>

		<div class="col">
			<h4 class="col-title">섹션</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/blog">전체 글</a></li>
				<li><a href="/blog?age=20-35">20–35세 · 유학·이민</a></li>
				<li><a href="/blog?age=35-55">35–55세 · 자산·자녀</a></li>
				<li><a href="/blog?age=55+">55세 이상 · 은퇴·건강</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="col">
			<h4 class="col-title">정보</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/about">편집실 소개</a></li>
				<li><a href="/rss.xml">RSS 피드</a></li>
				<li><a href="/sitemap-index.xml">사이트맵</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="col col-disclaimer">
			<h4 class="col-title">알림</h4>
			<p>본 사이트의 정보는 일반 정보 제공 목적이며, 법률·세무·의료 자문이 아닙니다. 구체적 상황은 전문가와 상담하시기 바랍니다.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container colophon">
		<span>© {today.getFullYear()} 미국 스토리. All rights reserved.</span>
		<span class="published">PUBLISHED IN THE UNITED STATES · 미국에서 발행</span>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer {
		background: var(--paper);
		border-top: 3px double var(--ink);
		padding: var(--s-5) 0 var(--s-3);
		margin-top: var(--s-7);
		color: var(--ink-soft);
		position: relative;
	}
	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr 1.6fr;
		gap: var(--s-4);
		padding-bottom: var(--s-4);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}
	.col-title {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: var(--text-xs);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		color: var(--brick);
		margin: 0 0 var(--s-2);
	}
	.col ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
	.col li { margin-bottom: 0.45em; }
	.col a {
		color: var(--ink-soft);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		line-height: 1.5;
		display: inline-block;
		border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
		transition: all var(--duration) var(--ease-out);
	}
	.col a:hover { color: var(--brick); border-bottom-color: var(--brick); }

	.masthead-mark { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; margin-bottom: var(--s-2); }
	.brand-ko {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--ink);
		line-height: 1;
	}
	.brand-en {
		font-size: 0.6rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.4em;
		color: var(--brick);
	}
	.tagline {
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--ink-medium);
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
		max-width: 18em;
	}

	.col-disclaimer p {
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--ink-light);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.colophon {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding-top: var(--s-3);
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		color: var(--ink-light);
		gap: var(--s-3);
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.published { color: var(--brick); }

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
	}
	@media (max-width: 540px) {
		.footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.colophon { flex-direction: column; gap: var(--s-1); text-align: center; }
	}
</style>
